WEBVTT

00:01:59.034 --> 00:02:00.354
tiklashiga imkon beruvchi

00:02:00.354 --> 00:02:02.124
metodlar ustida ishlamoqdamiz.

00:02:02.124 --> 00:02:03.374
Ularning ba'zilari beton-

00:02:03.374 --> 00:02:04.744
ning o'zini o'zi
tiklashining

00:02:04.744 --> 00:02:06.854
tabiiy mexanizmiga asoslangan.

00:02:06.859 --> 00:02:09.119
Kichik yoriqlar ichiga suv kirganida,

00:02:09.119 --> 00:02:12.109
u beton tarkibidagi 
kalsiy oksidini to'yintiradi.

00:02:12.109 --> 00:02:13.979
Havoda hosil bo'lgan kalsiy gidroksidi

00:02:13.979 --> 00:02:16.379
karbonat angidrid bilan 
reaksiyaga kirishadi va

00:02:16.379 --> 00:02:17.789
autogen tiklanish jarayoni

00:02:17.789 --> 00:02:19.559
boshlanadi: kalsiy karbonatining

00:02:19.559 --> 00:02:21.819
mayda kristallari hosil bo'lib,

00:02:21.819 --> 00:02:24.259
bo'shliqlarni to'ldira boshlaydi.

00:02:24.259 --> 00:02:26.159
Afsuski, bu kristallar

00:02:26.159 --> 00:02:28.749
0,3 mm gacha hajmdagi

00:02:28.749 --> 00:02:31.729
yoriqlarnigina yopishi mumkin.
